        <!-- About Text Content -->
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>About Adel Shakal</h2>
            <p>Adel Shakal is a distinguished professional in his field, known for his innovative contributions and expertise. With a career spanning over several years, Adel has worked on numerous projects that have made significant impacts. He is passionate about technology, constantly learning, and dedicated to bringing new solutions to the industry.</p>
            <p>In addition to his technical skills, Adel is highly regarded for his leadership and dedication to mentoring the next generation of professionals. He frequently engages in industry events and has contributed to many published works, further establishing his authority in the field.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer class="footer">
